## Before pushing dependency or Docker changes

- Will `npm ci` work on **Linux**? (not just Windows)
- Does Dockerfile deps stage avoid `prisma generate` before schema copy?
- Run `npm run lint` and `npm run typecheck` in `frontend/` if you changed TS

